<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You're Invited to PolicyPal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .tagline {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .invite-message {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features h3 {
            color: #495057;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .features ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .features li {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">PolicyPal</div>
            <div class="tagline">Smart Policy Management Platform</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>You're Invited to Join PolicyPal!</h2>
            
            <p>Hello,</p>
            
            <p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join PolicyPal, the smart policy management platform that helps organizations create, manage, and analyze their policies with AI-powered insights.</p>

            {{#if message}}
            <div class="invite-message">
                <strong>Personal Message:</strong><br>
                {{message}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="features">
                <h3>What you'll get with PolicyPal:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>ü§ñ AI-powered policy analysis and compliance checking</li>
                    <li>üìä Comprehensive analytics and reporting</li>
                    <li>üîí Data Loss Prevention (DLP) scanning</li>
                    <li>üõ°Ô∏è Privacy compliance and GDPR tools</li>
                    <li>üìù Smart policy templates and suggestions</li>
                    <li>üë• Collaborative policy management</li>
                    <li>üìß Automated notifications and reminders</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{inviteLink}}" class="cta-button">Accept Invitation & Sign Up</a>
            </div>

            <div class="expiry-notice">
                ‚è∞ This invitation link will expire in {{expiryDays}} days. Please accept the invitation soon to secure your account.
            </div>

            <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #007bff;">{{inviteLink}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This invitation was sent by {{inviterName}} through PolicyPal.</p>
            <p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 PolicyPal. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
